                            }
                        ],
                        "text": "When an ancient tupilaq is created, the curse imparted by its creator manifests in the form of a single 5th-rank primal spell the ancient tupilaq can cast three times per day. The particular spell is a reflection of the creator's wish for vengeance. By default, and for a found or summoned ancient tupilaq, this spell is *fireball*.",
